%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CodeFlare
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>opendatahub namespace
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>Dashboard 8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(220, 235, 250)
        Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: RayCluster Lifecycle
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (RayCluster)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + head-svc<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods + headless-svc<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route/Ingress (if enabled)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Autoscaler SA + Role + RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    end

    rect rgb(220, 250, 220)
        Note over User,Client: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (RayJob)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (if needed)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Note over Operator,RayHead: Wait for cluster ready
        Operator->>RayHead: POST /api/jobs/<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext, No Auth
        RayHead-->>Operator: Job ID
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create submitter K8s Job<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        loop Poll job status
            Operator->>RayHead: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext
            RayHead-->>Operator: Job status
        end
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    end

    rect rgb(250, 240, 220)
        Note over User,Client: Flow 3: RayService Serve Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayService CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (RayService)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Note over Operator,RayHead: Wait for cluster ready
        Operator->>RayHead: PUT /api/serve/applications/<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext, No Auth
        RayHead-->>Operator: Deployment status
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/update serve Service (8000/TCP)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        Client->>Workers: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8000, plaintext
        Workers-->>Client: Inference response
    end
